                       COMPUTE WK-EXHS-RT
                             = XDJL4124-O-PRVIUS-AMUS(WK-CUR-CNT) /
                               XDJL4124-O-LAST-INLS-LIMT(WK-CUR-CNT)

                       COMPUTE XDJL4124-O-EXHS-RT(WK-CUR-CNT)
                             = FUNCTION MAX(
                               FUNCTION MIN(
                               WK-EXHS-RT * 100, 999.99), 0)
      *@           그렇지않은경우　０으로　산출
